title: Ex-Senator Saif Magsi calls on prime minister
content:
ISLAMABAD, Aug 16 (APP): Former Senator Saif Magsi on Wednesday called on Caretaker Prime Minister Anwaar-ul-Haq Kakar here.
Saif Magsi congratulated the prime minister on assuming the office and expressed good wishes.
The prime minister thanked Saif Magsi for the wishes.
